txt.en: Confront High Priest Dáuraga and High Priestess Khôkali

The Order of the Eye descended into the Abyss of Mordath to defeat the Firehorns and seek the lost artifacts of the Dark Lord, but instead they have found secrets more terrible than they dared imagine.

The Order of the Eye descended into the Abyss of Mordath to defeat the Firehorns and seek the lost artifacts of the Dark Lord, but instead they have found secrets more terrible than they dared imagine.
Defeat High Priest Dáuraga and High Priestess Khôkali after allowing them to harness the essence of each of the Spoiled
You and your fellows must allow the High Priest and High Priestess of the Order of the Eye to harness the essence of each of the Spoiled before defeating them.
